  "title": "WAREHOUSE WORKERS @ JURONG EAST | FROM $2K | AIR CONDITIONED ENVIRONMENT",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>WAREHOUSE WORKERS @ JURONG EAST | FROM $2K | AIR CONDITIONED ENVIRONMENT </strong></u></p><p>📍Location: Jurong East </p><p>💰Salary: $2,000-$2,100 </p><p>🗓️Working days: Mon-Fri </p><p>🕑Shift hours:  8am-5pm </p><p>Job role: </p><ul><li><p>Manage receiving, checking, storing, and issuing of materials and finished goods using the ERP system with high accuracy. </p></li><li><p>Conduct regular inventory cycle counts and stock takes to ensure accurate and up-to-date inventory records. </p></li><li><p>Maintain proper housekeeping, systematic storage, and efficient use of warehouse space while adhering to safety standards. </p></li><li><p>Prepare shipping documents and pack finished goods according to standard packing, labeling, and operating procedures. </p></li></ul><p>Requirements:  </p><ul><li><p>2 years of experience in store or warehouse  </p></li><li><p>Physically strong enough to carry heavy loads </p></li></ul><p>📥Interested? Send us your resume at 8032 2021 or email: admin@crew.sg </p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary. </p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified </p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet </p><p>EA 24C2435 </p>",
